title: Grateful Dead Live at The Centrum on 1987-04-03
description:
Set 1

Hell In a Bucket-> Sugaree, C.C. Rider, It Must Have Been the Roses, It's All Over Now, Big Railroad Blues, Let It Grow-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Women Are Smarter-> Crazy Fingers-> Samson & Delilah-> Drums-> Space-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: U.S. Blues
